  "notes": "The tools we have today are incredibly powerful. Agentic capabilities across Azure and GitHub are already changing what’s possible with application and data modernization. Where many organizations still struggle is not with the tooling itself—but with turning those capabilities into consistent, repeatable execution across environments, workloads, and teams.\n \nThat’s where the Cloud Accelerate Factory comes in. It’s a dedicated Microsoft team, providing hands‑on delivery execution at no cost. Our differentiation isn’t limited to the innovation in our tools—it’s also the delivery model behind them. We invest Microsoft delivery capacity to help accelerate projects, reduce execution risk, and increase confidence for both customers and partners.\n \nThis execution model applies across a wide range of scenarios. Whether you’re modernizing applications and databases, strengthening resiliency and security, operationalizing agent workflows, or transforming data and analytics, the Factory brings structured delivery, reusable patterns, and expert, hands‑on execution.\n \nThe end result is that agentic innovation becomes real and repeatable. The Cloud Accelerate Factory turns tools like Azure Copilot and GitHub Copilot into production‑ready outcomes—combining automation with guardrails, consistency, and zero‑cost delivery support. That means faster time to value, lower risk, and a clear path to modernizing at scale."
}